
### `.gitignore` - المسار: `/.gitignore`
```gitignore
# Dependencies
node_modules/
.pnp/
.pnp.js

# Env
.env
.env.local
.env*.local

# Build
dist/
build/
out/
.next/
.vercel

# Logs
logs/
*.log
npm-debug.log*

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# IDE
.vscode/
.idea/

# Prisma
*.db
*.db-journal

# Redis / BullMQ
dump.rdb

# Docker
*.pid